channel.title: I'm really confused and I need help please!
channel.description: Okay, so here is the problem: I don't have and can't download Hamachi. So I'm trying to find a server that doesn't use it... Can someone give me one that doesn't use Hamachi and tell me how I can play on it... I mean I have the Moparscape window opened, but every single time I try and play on someones server, it says Error Connecting to server. Must be down... And I'm really frusterated b/c I've been trying this for like a week now, so can someone walk me through it or somthing?
